<D>__{i will find your table in a moment. braddock. not braniff? we have a braniff.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{no actually i'm just looking for a friend.}
<C>__{mrs. singleman}
<D>__{i'm afraid i don't understand.}
<C>__{ben}
<P>__{(backing off)}
<D>__{i'm not with your party i'm sorry.}
<C>__{mrs. singleman}
<D>__{hey i don't get it.}
<A>__{ben is backing out.}
<D>__{miss dewitte i've enjoyed meeting you, mr. braniff.}
<C>__{mrs. singleman}
<D>__{angela please!}
